Package edu.rit.teamwin.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AppointmentNotDuringBusinessHoursException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.validateAppointment when a given appointment trying to be scheduled does not occur during business hours.
    AppointmentNotValidException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.validateAppoint( appointment ) when a given appointment Id cannot be found in the database.
    ItemNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.getItemByKey when a given primary key filter could not be found in a given table.
    MaximumAppointmentCapacityReachedException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.generateId when the database cannot take any more new appointments.
    PhlebotomistNotAvailableException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.validateAppointment when a given appointment trying to be scheduled requests a phlebotomist that is already in an appointment.
    PhlebotomistTravelAvailabilityException
    This exception is thrown in the by LaboratoryAppointmentManager.validateAppointment when a given appointment trying to be scheduled requests a phlebotomist that will not make it from his/her current PSC to the requested PSC.
